World Championship Arabian Horse Show Salon Du Cheval De Paris

Start Date/Time: 30/11/13
End Date/Time: 01/12/13
Location: France
Category: Breeding & Show

Al Shaqab Breeding and Show Department shall participate in the World Championship Arabian Horse Show Salon Du Cheval De Paris in Paris, France, from 30 November to 1 December 2013.

To find out more about events at Al Shaqab, please click here.
